  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Insanity<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2525570/extras/13dc47fc6f4b391d901cbc18d548d569.avif?t=1769884765\" width=548 height=160 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2525570/extras/f8f5599d8e1b7d54cfce29c7ea73afc9.avif?t=1769884765\" width=548 height=160 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2525570/extras/21a560b48079a59e4bb1ea6ca48594bd.avif?t=1769884765\" width=548 height=160 /></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Two playable characters.<br>Each with their own maneuverability advantages and disadvantages.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Dropped into a strange world left to be lost and confused.  </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Don't expect the same old formula.  You will be lonely and left to explore a strange world.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >A mystery to unfold to find something pleasantly different.  </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Top-Down exploration merged with 2D platforming exploration</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Explore a large variety of top-down environments</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Collect items & power-ups</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Traverse a large variety of platforming landscapes</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Solve a large variety of puzzles</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Find hidden secrets</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Survive all threats</p></li></ul>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Insanity<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2525570/extras/13dc47fc6f4b391d901cbc18d548d569.avif?t=1769884765\" width=548 height=160 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2525570/extras/f8f5599d8e1b7d54cfce29c7ea73afc9.avif?t=1769884765\" width=548 height=160 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2525570/extras/21a560b48079a59e4bb1ea6ca48594bd.avif?t=1769884765\" width=548 height=160 /></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Two playable characters.<br>Each with their own maneuverability advantages and disadvantages.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Dropped into a strange world left to be lost and confused.  </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Don't expect the same old formula.  You will be lonely and left to explore a strange world.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >A mystery to unfold to find something pleasantly different.  </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Top-Down exploration merged with 2D platforming exploration</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Explore a large variety of top-down environments</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Collect items & power-ups</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Traverse a large variety of platforming landscapes</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Solve a large variety of puzzles</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Find hidden secrets</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Survive all threats</p></li></ul>",
